message.body: Brett just called - gonna unload a tabel and then I call u back
No problem

Kk
Baby sorry about last night. I wasn't as graceful as I would have liked to be. You know I love you and that I don't think you're doing anything wrong (even
Though we shouldn't have to rationalize the relationship!). I hope you're have a swell thursday. I know you're probably not as excited but once you get to
Philly you're going to love it!! Plus I can't wait for u to visit. I love my new neighborhood!

I appreciate that but don't apologize. Right or wrong; rationalized or not; this is almost impossible to navigate. I just expect you to temper any of your reactions or thoughts for me. We're both processing out loud probably, and the fact that you give me the opportunity to do that is all I can ask for.
